Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:10.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Three of the Detective Boys have spent their\Nsummer vacation enthralled by a new video game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:16.26,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After talking to a fellow Teitan Elementary student\Nthat we bumped into at a convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.74,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}we ended up going over to his\Nrelative’s place to play the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.37,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I sensed something suspicious about the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.71,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But just then, Toshinari-{\i1}san{\i0} made a grisly\Ndiscovery in the apartment next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:36.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Elsewhere, there was another surprise\Nbetween Detectives Sato and Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m missing my you-know-what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed?! You don’t mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:48.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s embarrassing, so don’t tell anyone, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miwako is having a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happy news!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.97,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We won’t give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.41,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Detective Takagi’s gonna be a daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.41,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A shocking trick that startles the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:06.87,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.56,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:11.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
